overview: CDG Business Systems, Inc., established in 2005, is a nationwide Preferred Channel Partner for Hewlett-Packard “Diversity Certified”, Dell Premier, Lenovo, and Cisco. Additionally, we are partnered with Samsung, Toshiba, Novell, Ricoh and top industry software providers, such as, Microsoft, Oracle, Adobe, Symantec, VM Ware, McAfee, Trend Micro, to name a few. CDG Business Systems, Inc., have certified account executives, technicians and an array of support staff to assist you with any of your IT solution needs.
